ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啪啪聲唔係D骨啪，係關節啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會啪我唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該都係太重/姿態唔岩？<br />\n<br />\n你想要睇體質應該去搵中醫，營養學冇分呢D，最多都係同你試點樣食法你自己最舒服又食得夠蛋白質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少食多餐最基本，正餐中間飲杯奶食隻蛋咁<br />\n再勁D可以用奶開奶粉，極營養<br />\n但前提都係你要做運動，唔係嘅話食多左都係變脂肪變唔到肌肉就冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fd849f9ed305f9dcd18632aa47717cf32f5734","tid":2408824,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"........懶,唔自律.<br />\n自己控制啦. 慳唔少"},{"pid":"46164192eb076e51f3bd9ff5936afbfda6d72258","tid":2408824,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"乜減肥要另外比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"fd8f20f77eec07035aca7d8aceb133bcb7197a2a","tid":2408824,"uid":152498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d764a68626437beea0cb35263ad202df3e5e5627","tid":2408824,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d877eab9bd54492ae313129d1f606660bc4d01ff","tid":2408824,"uid":152498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23596bbf3a1eb77721df92b3d394cffc506de933","tid":2408824,"uid":273953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"做負重運動可以增加骨質密度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會整親一係就姿勢唔岩<br />\n一係就太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都好少係傷骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有野都係要慢慢黎架啦<br />\n食野不外乎少食多餐，食多啲高蛋白質食物，食少啲冇營養嘅野，冇咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:28:27.000Z","msg":"我d骨成日都啪啪聲 可以自己唔夠鈣 又冇乜脂肪 搞到我有咁既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食野無錯都係個d大路野 但我想seek多d專業既建議 例如體質 點樣吸收 營養品份量控制 上網有好多 但我驚唔啱自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"骨係用肌肉包唔係用脂肪包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啪啪聲唔係D骨啪，係關節啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會啪我唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該都係太重/姿態唔岩？<br />\n<br />\n你想要睇體質應該去搵中醫，營養學冇分呢D，最多都係同你試點樣食法你自己最舒服又食得夠蛋白質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少食多餐最基本，正餐中間飲杯奶食隻蛋咁<br />\n再勁D可以用奶開奶粉，極營養<br />\n但前提都係你要做運動，唔係嘅話食多左都係變脂肪變唔到肌肉就冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />了解<br />\n中醫細過睇過 冇乜成效 個人虛但中醫d野又太補<br />\n<br />\n飲奶加蛋試過阿.. 個時飲太多搞到個人熱氣 又皮膚敏感爆晒瘡 同埋本身腸胃唔好 奶製既野好易屙 <br />\n<br />\n同埋我而家唔知有痛風定類風濕關節炎, 仲check 緊飄鈴/大豆制食物都儘量少掂 太多制肘搞到我都唔知點行好 又覺得一路below BMI margin 年紀再大d 會出事..<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}